Package com.deloitte.capi.transformers

This package contains Anypoint Java Transformers used throughout the application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExecutionDriverTransformer
    This class is used to generate data (Java objects) that will be used to drive execution of the overall API.
    HCHandlingTransformer
    Anypoint Java Transformer that is executed after calls to the Health Canada API, to combine the returned data with the Source data.
    TweetHandlingTransformer
    Anypoint Java Transformer that is executed after calls to the Twitter API, to combine the returned data with the Source data.
    TwitterConnector
    Java code to connect to the Twitter API, using OAuth security.

Package com.deloitte.capi.transformers Description
